of the situation.

273
00:14:17,916 --> 00:14:21,484
I understand that, we
have a lot in common.

274
00:14:22,921 --> 00:14:23,921
Is that so?

275
00:14:25,365 --> 00:14:28,441
- [soft music]
- [crickets chirp]

276
00:14:28,593 --> 00:14:30,184
I better got to bed.

277
00:14:30,278 --> 00:14:32,537
- Goodnight.
- Goodnight.

278
00:14:32,688 --> 00:14:34,497
- [soft music]
- [crickets chirp]

279
00:14:38,861 --> 00:14:43,631
- [soft, ominous music]
- [crickets chirp]

280
00:15:09,242 --> 00:15:11,721
Hey, how'd the
nanny interview go?

281
00:15:11,745 --> 00:15:14,987
It went really well,
we've already hired her.

282
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:16,730
Wow, that was fast.

283
00:15:16,824 --> 00:15:18,374
It was ella's decision, really.

284
00:15:20,754 --> 00:15:24,380
- So, show me the book.
- Oh, yes.

285
00:15:28,486 --> 00:15:29,486
Wow.

