to man the grill.

516
00:27:49,669 --> 00:27:51,835
[laughs]

517
00:27:57,902 --> 00:27:59,009
Mind if I join you?

518
00:28:00,587 --> 00:28:02,565
- Sure.
- Thanks.

519
00:28:02,589 --> 00:28:04,807
