00:35:06,438 --> 00:35:08,087
- Jack!
- What?

664
00:35:08,181 --> 00:35:10,165
- What was that about?
- What?

665
00:35:10,258 --> 00:35:11,569
The way you were
talking to David,

666
00:35:11,593 --> 00:35:12,995
Why are you being so rude?

667
