anything around here.

671
00:35:21,845 --> 00:35:22,869
It's all about you.

672
00:35:24,865 --> 00:35:25,914
Enjoy your party.

673
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:31,536
- [light music]
- [birds chirp]

