00:35:31,630 --> 00:35:34,256
[dramatic music]

675
00:35:37,803 --> 00:35:40,857
[crickets chirp]

676
00:35:40,881 --> 00:35:42,117
[Remy] I can't
believe you did that.

677
00:35:42,141 --> 00:35:43,473
What?

678
00:35:43,700 --> 00:35:45,049
