In front of everybody?

680
00:35:46,979 --> 00:35:48,698
Do you know how
that made me look?

681
00:35:48,722 --> 00:35:50,730
[jack] right, so I
screwed up, again.

682
00:35:52,967 --> 00:35:54,985
