- Right.

691
00:36:20,995 --> 00:36:23,588
I'll leave you alone so
you can get some sleep.

692
00:36:23,682 --> 00:36:26,016
Jack, please.

693
00:36:27,019 --> 00:36:30,312
[soft, dramatic music]

694
00:36:32,098 --> 00:36:34,024
[sighs]

695
00:36:43,702 --> 00:36:45,994
