out when I get back, okay?

714
00:37:35,754 --> 00:37:37,754
- Whatever you want.
- Good morning.

715
00:37:39,091 --> 00:37:41,383
I'm sorry, I can
go back upstairs.

716
00:37:42,744 --> 00:37:44,427
No, no, you don't
have to do that.

717
00:37:45,913 --> 00:37:48,598
Everything here is
fine, right, honey?

718
00:37:51,678 --> 00:37:52,678
Just fine.

719
00:37:54,422 --> 00:37:55,438
I'll see you later.

720
00:37:57,350 --> 00:37:59,087
