732
00:38:59,229 --> 00:39:03,840
- [sighs]
- [soft, ominous music]

733
00:39:18,098 --> 00:39:22,859
- [sighs]
- [soft, ominous music]

734
00:39:37,434 --> 00:39:42,170
- [laughs]
