1366
01:17:15,539 --> 01:17:17,184
What do you want?

1367
01:17:17,208 --> 01:17:20,020
I'll give you anything,
just please don't hurt her.

1368
01:17:20,044 --> 01:17:21,636
What do I want?

1369
01:17:21,787 --> 01:17:24,546
- What do I want?
- Yes, anything.

1370
